{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_01","textHome":"唔，想尽量了解和我相关的事情，就这些。@嗯？还不行吗。这样啊……@没有爱好，喜欢的词汇是公平和平等。@虽然不容易看出来，但想当一个温柔的姐姐。@还有，以前划分在东边这一带，@和七海、梓有过激烈的竞争。差不多就这样。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_18","textHome":"拍照吗？我也能挣到钱，当然可以。@不过市里认识我的人有点多，@抱歉还是让我遮一下脸吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_19","textHome":"又获得了一种能用来实现公平的力量了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"id":101600}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_20","textHome":"唔，脱胎换骨的感觉。@回去的路上逮个魔女试试。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":200}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_21","textHome":"做了魔法少女，位于人上的事情就多起来了。@别人来寻求帮助这一点，倒也不坏。@毕竟能够在狩猎魔女以外的事情上帮到别人。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_22","textHome":"魔法少女在共同的宿命之上是平等的。@无论生于何方，成为魔法少女的瞬间，@就背负了同样的重担。我会为成长而喜悦，@也是为了守护那样的同胞们。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":9.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_23","textHome":"毁灭神滨，是我对故乡最大的爱。@但是，没有能实现的办法。@所以第二层的爱，就是最大限度地守护它。@为此我要变强。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_24","textHome":"难得光临，我已等候多时了。@今天是否准备好了自己的拿手好活？@……唔，那么就快走吧！@去捕捉海的乐趣！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":400}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_25","textHome":"唔，刚好起来那麻烦你了，@能帮忙把这玩意的内脏去了吗？@是今早刚钓上的鱼，@新鲜又好吃。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_26","textHome":"唔，嗯……虽然一直觉得很贵，@但海之家的料理好吃得不可思议，令人叹服。@但是，确实很贵。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":200}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_27","textHome":"夏天的夕阳，正如窥视过去的窗户……@让人回想起曾经在八云那看见的寂寞背影……@我记得那天，也正是一个夏天的傍晚时分……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101600}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_03","textHome":"我很少和他人这样说话，请你用心听。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_28","textHome":"平时的这个时间，已经结束了兼职，@在回家路上了。吹着宁静的晚风，@幸福得仿佛要生出罪恶感一样，真是奇妙。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":100,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_29","textHome":"来吧，下海之前的准备运动！@半蹲着张开双手，从捕获猎物的运动做起！@一二三，做手势！二二三，做手势！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":400}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_30","textHome":"至少休息希望能安稳点啊。@然而感知到魔女就不得不去解决了。@唔，我就穿着泳装去也无妨。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_31","textHome":"其实泳装有着惊人的活动性……@去无尽镜界练练手好了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":1}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":9.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_32","textHome":"在这样的暑气中大批人集中起来对抗，@真是我无法想象的事情。@先在这里看看情况吧，@急于出击不是上策。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":300}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_33","textHome":"你知道「变美味」的咒语吗？@只要念着这个，主人就会觉得什么都好吃了。@比如这盘海藻就可以试试。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":200}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_34","textHome":"啊，怎么可能……@第一节课就是游泳的话，这应该很正常吧……@不是吗？里面穿着泳装来上学不对劲吗……？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_35","textHome":"如何，是不是浑身激灵很舒服？@热的时候就像这样把冷的水瓶@夹在腋下、大腿和脖子上是很好用的。@还能节约电费。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.5,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_36","textHome":"像是渔人和海员，@在海上劳动的大人们看着就很伟岸。@当然在海之家劳作的人也不例外。@劳动者的汗水是最美丽的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_37","textHome":"唔，泳装的价格压得很低了。@要说起来，还是八云的功劳。@虽然被她尽情玩了一番，@但也确实很努力的帮我选了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_04","textHome":"我们至今都一直被过去绊住了脚步。"}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_38","textHome":"我有个想法。@你觉得海边的女仆咖啡厅怎么样？@感觉能成为工作日和假日兼顾的店铺，@找机会跟姐姐大人说说看吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":300}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_39","textHome":"像这样，噗咕噗咕噗咕——哈。@曾经和家人一起去海边的时候，@父亲是这样教我游泳的。@想起来都觉得心中很温暖。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_40","textHome":"就算遇险也不用担心。@别看我这样，@足以保命的生存术也还是会的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_51_41","textHome":"到处都有情侣傍若无人地在卿卿我我啊……@唔……@仔细一想，我和七海还有梓她们@到了能结婚的年纪了没有啊……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":300}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_42","textHome":"东边的调停者，登场！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":400}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_43","textHome":"该说越发进步了吗？"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_44","textHome":"店长打电话来了，得马上去店里！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_45","textHome":"生死是平等地给予我们的权利。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_46","textHome":"为自己的行动感到痛心，而后偿还吧。"}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_63","textHome":"如果想动手那就过来！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_05","textHome":"虽然空虚，但也无可奈何……@因为这座城市里只有舍弃的理由……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_64","textHome":"别太直接，我已看穿一切！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":400}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_65","textHome":"抱歉，我将给予你们独一无二的平等！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_66","textHome":"生与死，你将去向何方？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_02","textHome":"想借助我和泉十七夜的力量的人，就是你吗？@但这句话是否真心，@就由我窥探你的内心来确定吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":101600,"motion":400}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_13","textHome":"唔，感觉不错。这就是鞭策出来的气势吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_14","textHome":"以前就受八云的关照，现在更是如此了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_15","textHome":"每句话都读一遍你的内心，这样也不介意吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_16","textHome":"变美味♪变美味♪这样真的会变好吃吗？@唔，把这个树桩蛋糕拿去给主人试试吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group